      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura movimento su file                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       scr-mov-fil-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento file [zcs]                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se inserimento                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to scr-mov-fil-500.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Write record [zcs]                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-zcs-000      thru wrt-rec-zcs-999        .
           go to     scr-mov-fil-999.
       scr-mov-fil-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se modifica                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Rewrite record [zcs]                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   rew-rec-zcs-000      thru rew-rec-zcs-999        .
       scr-mov-fil-999.
           exit.

